âœ¨ Features
Transaction Management
âœ… Add Transactions - Income and expense tracking with categories

âœ… Edit Transactions - Modify existing entries

âœ… Delete Transactions - Remove unwanted entries with confirmation

âœ… Transaction History - Complete list with filtering options

âœ… Categories - Food, Travel, Bills, Shopping, Entertainment, Health, Salary, Freelance, Other

âœ… Notes - Add optional descriptions to transactions

Budget Trackingâ€‹
ðŸ’° Set Budgets - Weekly or monthly limits per category

ðŸ“Š Visual Progress Bars - Real-time spending visualization

âš ï¸ Smart Alerts - Warnings when approaching (>80%) or exceeding budget

ðŸ”´ Overspending Indicators - Clear visual feedback with color coding

ðŸ“ˆ Automatic Calculations - Spent amount auto-updates with new transactions

Dashboard & Analytics
ðŸ  Home Overview - Total balance, income, and expenses at a glance

ðŸ“… Recent Transactions - Last 5 transactions on home screen

ðŸŽ¯ Budget Alerts - Priority warnings for budget issues

ðŸ’¹ Real-time Calculations - Instant balance updates

User Experienceâ€‹
ðŸ“± Bottom Tab Navigation - Intuitive 4-tab structure (Home, Transactions, Budget, More)

ðŸŽ¨ Clean UI/UX - Material Design-inspired interface

ðŸ’¾ Offline-First - All data stored locally, works without internet

âš¡ Fast Performance - Optimized rendering with React Context

ðŸ”’ Data Privacy - All data stays on your device

